Author: AlgoryProject
Title: [ANN][ICO] ALGORY - Multifunctional Tools For Cryptocurrency Traders
Body: Cryptonews – the largest aggregator of news from the world of cryptocurrencies has been launched       Algory is delighted to announce the launch of the largest news system for investors and crypto-traders on the cryptocurrencies market – the Cryptonews aggregator. We are pleased to announce that one of our flagship products is live and that we have succeeded.  The Cryptonews system will enable users to track all information from around the world affecting the volatility of the price of cryptocurrencies.   Cryptonews filters information coming from thematic websites, blogs, companies focused on the cryptocurrency industry, companies focused on the blockchain technology industry. It also analyzes data from social media, which have a significant impact on volatility in the cryptocurrency market.  At current moment, we have connected to the system the top 1,000 of various types of news sources from the world of cryptocurrencies. Speed is important in trading. Our system provides traders with a solution such as "all cryptonews in one place", thanks to which they will no longer have to browse dozens of other websites or tools. And soon our next product will appear on the market – Cryptoscanner. Tomasz Przybycień, Co-founder of Algory   The best place for cryptoheads to stay up to date Users of the platform will have the option of creating dedicated workspaces. The platform's customers will be able to sort the news according to their needs, the cryptocurrencies or the news category of their interest. There will also be archival data available, thanks to which investors from the cryptocurrency market will be able to assess which sources of information had the greatest impact on the volatility of exchange rates.  Currently, access to the news platform is offered for free. In the future, a premium version will be launched, in which, for a fee, users will get access to the VIP features.   Algory Cryptonews is now one of the most competitive major crypto news aggregator in the world. However, we want to remind you that this is only the beginning, there is a lot more work to be done. So subsequent announcements about new tools will follow.   About Algory Algory is a startup based in Katowice in Poland. Algory offers tools for active crypto traders. The flagship products include an advanced cryptocurrency scanner, called Cryptoscanner, and a crypto news aggregator, which was designed for the most active traders. Official website: https://algory.io

Body: Dear altcointalk14,  you don't need to highlight your questions in red.   Regarding unsold tokens, we informed about it in our article on Medium during the crowdsale:   Due to numerous questions regarding unsold tokens, please be informed that we are considering two possibilities for their further use:  Option one  The first option is to leave some of them (and burn the rest) to complete a post-sale later (in at least a couple of months) to ensure further financing into the company when we develop new key features for the products.  In this option — the amount (based on current ETH price) will not be great than 20–30% of unsold tokend. Rest will be burnt.  Option two  The second possibility considered by the company is to burn all tokens if the revenues of the company resulting from Premium access to the Algory platform are at a level that enables further fast growth of the project. Author: tsg
Title: [ANN][ICO] ALGORY - Multifunctional Tools For Cryptocurrency Traders
Body: There's a new article about Algory next feature on Medium!   Do you buy tops and sell bottoms?   Algory Project: Cryptocurrency backtester — Backtest your trading strategy!  Backtesting is a key component in the creation of the most efficient trading strategy possible on the cryptocurrency market.  How Backtester works  After setting the proper filters in the scanner, you will be able to move on to the Backtester functions. You will need to fill in some information, based upon which an appropriate simulation will be prepared. In the following example, the filters/alerts defined had the following assumptions:  Symbol searched: BTCUSD Filters: Volume ratio increase: 2 Alerts: Consolidation breakout/breakdown on 1-hour interval.  You will even be able to determine settings related to your own imperfection and slippages: -slippage -the value of stop loss % and $ -take profit value -the size of position/capital -exit time  In addition, you will be asked to set the time-frame in which you wish to conduct backtesting, even if you want to limit it to specific times of the day, you will also be able to do just that.

Author: AlgoryProject
Title: [ANN][ICO] ALGORY - Multifunctional Tools For Cryptocurrency Traders
Body: Cauchy,  the biggest change on the crypto market will be our CryptoScanner. Now, there is no such an advanced tool in existence. It will scan real-time all data from crypto exchanges and let you set hundreds of filerts/alerts in different time intervals. When you get a signal - you can use it and open position manually or connect it with the Autotrading system. But if you are not sure if your trading signals will be profitable - no problem, you can use Backterster. Our backtester will use historical data to check how profitable your strategy has been in the past.  Article about CryptoScanner: https://medium.com/algory-project/algory-project-functions-the-first-and-most-powerful-cryptocurrency-scanner-d681c3ce3c45  Secondly, you will have CryptoNews. There are some tools that provides news, but none of the you can connect with Autotrading system. You can choose keywords (i.e. "china", "ban") and try to be the first one who open/close position after important news. Additionally, our News System will also use the data from social media channels - you will be able to check the social media infuence on the market.  Please check the article about CryptoNews: https://medium.com/algory-project/algory-project-cryptonews-never-be-late-again-e63ebd90cf12  You can also check our Blockchain Analyzer and "trade like a whale" - it means, that Blockchain Analyzer will follow the biggest transfers between wallets (i.e. you will see that someone is transfering 200k ETH to big exchange = maybe you will see a sell-off there. You will be notified about it and see what happens later). And it is only one functionality of Blockchain Analyzer. It will provides much more important data from blockchains   And it is only the top of the Iceberg Check our official website: ALGORY. We have 13 advanced functions in our platform.

Title: [ANN][ICO] ALGORY - Multifunctional Tools For Cryptocurrency Traders
Body: Have you read our article about Cryptoscanner on Medium? If now, now is the best time to do this! Please check the details of functionality in our first feature!   We are pleased to announce that — through its ICO — Algory Project wishes to introduce a crypto-trading tool that will change the way you perceive trading. Today I would like to show you the first flagship functionality of Algory — Cryptoscanner.  “The idea for the tool was born at the beginning of 2017. It was a period when we really did a lot of trading in the cryptocurrency market, carrying out several dozen to several hundred transactions a day. We realized we did not have enough time to quickly and efficiently analyze the cryptocurrencies with the greatest potential to generate above-average profit. On the US stock exchanges in which I traded, such tools were present and practically all professional traders used them. I cannot imagine a trading office where nobody uses such a boon as a scanner.” — Dominik Gordel, Algory Project Cofounder.     There will be +100 different filters available on the platform. The short description is:  The users will find an exchange on which, after deducting transaction costs, they will buy a specific cryptocurrency at the best price and at the quickest pace, or sell it most profitably. Author: Yasemin
Title: [ANN][ICO] ALGORY - Multifunctional Tools For Cryptocurrency Traders
Body: You got a reply before, but I think you did not see it. Let me quote if for you:  Quote Jonnytracker,  Let's start with that: we are not a prediction market or bot that trade instead of traders.  We move methods for filtering data and news that we use when trading on Equity Markets.  So you can define different ways of filtering each cryptocurrencies listed on diffrent exchanges. You can filter news data from different sources. For example:  The trader is focused on finding consolidation breakouts which are the most effective when the breakout occurs on a turnover volume that is several times higher relative to its average turnover.  In that case, they will use several Cryptoscanner filters: 1. Price range of cryptocurrencies (possibility of choosing price in relation to BTC, ETH or fiats). 2. They will determine the average volume. 3. They will determine the volume ratio, i.e. how much the volume should increase. E.g. volume ratio 3 (3 times bigger than the average).  Then they will go to the alerts where they will choose: 1. Consolidation breakout – where they will determine at what intervals the prior consolidation had to be delineated.  When the criteria above are met, they will receive all information about the events that occurred in the scanner window:  The trader will be able to choose from a very wide range of 1. Filters 2. Alerts  In addition, they will be able to specify: 1. The cryptocurrency exchanges to be scanned. 2. A list of symbols that they would like to be scanned. 3. Enabling the auto-trading feature that will open/close positions based on pre-defined parameters. 4. Strategy backtesting to simulate its efficiency on the basis of its historical data.   This is just about Cryptoscanner. There are 12 more functions.   In next days/weeks we will be publishing articles about each functions - so you will be able find out more.

Title: [ANN][ICO] ALGORY - Multifunctional Tools For Cryptocurrency Traders
Body: Jay 2408, we do not have soft cap.   Quote from: jonnytracker on November 19, 2017, 02:01:33 PM every new project is revolutionary indeed.. how is this different from Napoleonx ?   Jonnytracker,  Let's start with that: we are not a prediction market or bot that trade instead of traders.  We move methods for filtering data and news that we use when trading on Equity Markets.  So you can define different ways of filtering each cryptocurrencies listed on diffrent exchanges. You can filter news data from different sources. For example:  The trader is focused on finding consolidation breakouts which are the most effective when the breakout occurs on a turnover volume that is several times higher relative to its average turnover.  In that case, they will use several Cryptoscanner filters: 1. Price range of cryptocurrencies (possibility of choosing price in relation to BTC, ETH or fiats). 2. They will determine the average volume. 3. They will determine the volume ratio, i.e. how much the volume should increase. E.g. volume ratio 3 (3 times bigger than the average).  Then they will go to the alerts where they will choose: 1. Consolidation breakout – where they will determine at what intervals the prior consolidation had to be delineated.  When the criteria above are met, they will receive all information about the events that occurred in the scanner window:  The trader will be able to choose from a very wide range of 1. Filters 2. Alerts  In addition, they will be able to specify: 1. The cryptocurrency exchanges to be scanned. 2. A list of symbols that they would like to be scanned. 3. Enabling the auto-trading feature that will open/close positions based on pre-defined parameters. 4. Strategy backtesting to simulate its efficiency on the basis of its historical data.   This is just about Cryptoscanner. There are 12 more functions.   In next days/weeks we will be publishing articles about each functions - so you will be able find out more.
